XPLOREU was created by student travelers who all had a backpack and a dream.  Now that the backpack is worn in and the dreams have been reached, we just can't shut up about them.
XU hopes to make the travel process more fulfilling and less confusing by being a one-stop portal to guide and connect students before they go abroad.  We believe that in order to truly understand your place in the world, you must first SEE and UNDERSTAND the world. We also want to travel vicariously through you.  Is that creepy?  Forget we said it.